            <thetext>Steps to reproduce:
- create an qx.ui.basic.Atom
- set label to a multi-line text
- set labelObject#setWrap to true
- set labelObject#textAlign to center
- set horizontalChildrenAlign to center
- set a bg color to make bounds of Atom visible

The text of the label should be centered but it is aligned to the right.
I&#39;ll provide a code attachment and a screen shot.</thetext>
